Usage: USERS [<channel>] [<wildcards>] [<options>] [<reason>]
  Performs some action on users matching the wildcards and options
  in a channel.  If no options are given, a list of users is shown
  instead.

  Valid options:
    -OPS    -- makes it only select ops
    -NONOPS -- makes it only select non-ops
    -KILL   -- kills users matching the pattern
    -MSG    -- sends a msg to all users matching the pattern
    -NOTICE -- sends a notice to all users matching the pattern
